           ┌─ Help ─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
           │ Probe Chat Shell Keys                                  │
           │                                                        │
           │ Tab / Shift+Tab     switch Chat / Setup / Events       │
           │ Enter / Ctrl+J      submit / newline                   │
           │ Ctrl+R / Ctrl+T     rerun setup / toggle detail        │
           │ F1 / Esc            toggle or dismiss help             │
           │ Ctrl+C              quit                               │
           │ Composer only runs while Chat owns focus.              │
           └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘




